text: Þis is se halidom ðe is on ðam grecysscan scrine ðe seo hlæfdige geaf into niwan mynstre.
Þæt is of Sancte Iohanne baptista, and of montem Sion, and of ðam stane þe se orod stod on uppan ðe ure dryhten on ðrowode.
And of þære binnan ðe ure dryhten onlæg, and ofmensa domini, and of þare gyrde þe Moyses hæfde ofer þa readan sæ.
And of ðare dune monte caluarie, andsepulchrum domini, and oflignum domini.
And of sanct<../images/etail.gif>Andre<../images/etail.gif>apostol<../images/etail.gif>, and of sancte Pancrate.
And of Melchisedech, and of sanct<../images/etail.gif>Uedaste, and of sancte Ypolite.
